---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import myImage from "../assets/about.jpg";
import SectionTitle from "./SectionTitle.astro";
---

<section class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-24" id="about">
    <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-12 gap-16 items-start">
      <!-- Image Container - Takes 5 columns -->
      <div class="lg:col-span-5 lg:sticky lg:top-24">
        <div class="relative mx-auto lg:mx-0">
          <div class="aspect-[4/5]">
            <Image
              src={myImage}
              alt="Jake Meyers - Full Stack & AI Developer"
              class="rounded-2xl shadow-xl w-full h-full object-cover object-top"
            />
          </div>
          <div
            class="absolute -z-10 -inset-4 bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-100 to-blue-50 rounded-2xl opacity-70 blur-2xl"
          >
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
  
      <!-- Text Container - Takes 7 columns -->
      <div class="lg:col-span-7 space-y-8">
        <SectionTitle title="About" />
        <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none text-gray-700">
          <p>
            Hi, I'm Jake Meyers, a freelance full-stack developer and AI specialist based in St. Louis, Missouri. I help businesses worldwide integrate artificial intelligence and build custom web applications. As an independent developer, I work directly with you to create tailored solutions that fit your specific needs and budget.
          </p>
  
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">What I Do</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-3">
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="flex-shrink-0 flex items-center justify-center w-6 h-6 mt-1 mr-3 bg-blue-100 rounded-full">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-blue-600" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
                </svg>
              </span>
              <span>
                <strong class="text-gray-900">AI Development:</strong> RAG applications, chatbots, MCP servers, and AI automation using OpenAI, Anthropic, and open-source models.
              </span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="flex-shrink-0 flex items-center justify-center w-6 h-6 mt-1 mr-3 bg-blue-100 rounded-full">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-blue-600" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
                </svg>
              </span>
              <span>
                <strong class="text-gray-900">Full-Stack Development:</strong> React, Next.js, Node.js, Python FastAPI, PostgreSQL, and modern deployment platforms.
              </span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="flex-shrink-0 flex items-center justify-center w-6 h-6 mt-1 mr-3 bg-blue-100 rounded-full">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-blue-600" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
                </svg>
              </span>
              <span>
                <strong class="text-gray-900">Learning on the Job:</strong> I stay current with emerging technologies and can quickly adapt to new frameworks and tools as your project needs evolve.
              </span>
            </li>
          </ul>
  
          <p class="mt-8">
            I love working at the intersection of AI and web development, creating solutions that are both technically sophisticated and practically useful. My approach combines technical depth with clear communication—I'll explain complex concepts in simple terms and keep you informed throughout the development process.
          </p>
  
          <p class="mt-4">
            While I'm based in St. Louis, Missouri, I work with clients worldwide. As a freelancer, you get direct access to me throughout your project—no account managers or middlemen. I pride myself on being responsive, transparent about timelines, and committed to delivering quality work that exceeds expectations.
          </p>
  
          <p class="mt-4">
            When I'm not coding or exploring the latest AI developments, you'll find me hiking the trails around St. Louis, experimenting with new tech stacks, or contributing to open-source projects. I believe the best developers never stop learning.
          </p>
  
          <div class="mt-12">
            
              <a href="#contact"
              class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-8 py-4 text-base font-medium text-white bg-blue-600 rounded-lg hover:bg-blue-700 transition-colors duration-200 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl"
            >
              Let's Work Together
              <svg
                xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                class="w-5 h-5"
                viewBox="0 0 20 20"
                fill="currentColor"
              >
                <path
                  fill-rule="evenodd"
                  d="M10.293 3.293a1 1 0 011.414 0l6 6a1 1 0 010 1.414l-6 6a1 1 0 01-1.414-1.414L14.586 11H3a1 1 0 110-2h11.586l-4.293-4.293a1 1 0 010-1.414z"
                  clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
              </svg>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>